install Composer (https://getcomposer.org/)
install PHPUnit (https://phpunit.de/)

Install sphinx
sudo apt-get install python-sphinx
sudo pip install sphinxcontrib-phpdomain

Generate rst files
sphpdox --output="<outputpath>"
namespace (<namespace> or "no-namespace" if namespaces are not used)

make html

Usefull links
https://pythonhosted.org/sphinxcontrib-phpdomain/index.html
http://sphinx-doc.org/tutorial.html
http://matplotlib.org/sampledoc/index.html
https://github.com/varspool/sphpdox

composer install